  the Ph-only tables (folding Trinity and alias pins), plus
  `kind=coordinate` wave vectors `WV-COORD-SATOSHI/V/FALSE`. The §2.1
  guarantee is now executable.
- **m3** (size metric prose): the review is right that the invariant line
  never tied `materialized_size(t)` to §3.4's Розмір definition — and
  right that no Synthetic Exclusion Lemma is needed (confirming the
  maintainer's Kimi refutation from the implementation side). §3.4 now
  says so in one sentence.
- **N1** (≥80-bit LUT demand vs IEEE-double oracle): confirmed
  self-inconsistency. §4 reworded — the arbiter hash is authoritative;
  64-bit provably suffices (no entry within 0.5 ULP of a tie).
- **N2** (coverage gaps): all three adopted — `EV-STUCK-DIS-FN`,
  `EV-STUCK-LIT-FN` (stuck normal forms at spent 4, exactly as the review
